OL,3,CGovernment scraps Devon warships HMS
OL,4,CAlbion and Bulwark
OL,6,FITV News' Lucy McDaid and Marina
OL,7,FJenkins bring this report from
OL,8,FWestminster and Plymouth
OL,10,FDevonport-based Royal Navy warships
OL,11,FHMS Albion, Bulwark and Northumberland
OL,12,Fare being axed.
OL,14,FThe Defence Secretary John Healey made
OL,15,Fthe announcement in the House of
OL,16,FCommons, saying Labour is facing
OL,17,F"serious financial pressures in the
OL,18,FDefence budget" and "immediate action"
OL,19,Fneeds to be taken.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
