PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F438A1732288151
OL,3,CGovernment scraps Devon warships HMS
OL,4,CAlbion and Bulwark
OL,6,F"Both are currently held at lower
OL,7,Freadiness having not been to sea since
OL,8,F2023 and 2017 respectively. On current
OL,9,Fplanning, neither was due to go to sea
OL,10,Fagain before their planned out of
OL,11,Fservice dates of 2033 and 2034. They
OL,12,Fhad, in effect, been mothballed, but
OL,13,Fwere still costing the taxpayer around
OL,14,F#9m per year to maintain."
OL,16,FMr Healey added: "I have halted the
OL,17,Fcurrent refit of HMS Northumberland, a
OL,18,FType 23 frigate, which will now be
OL,19,Fretired from the Fleet in March 2025."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
