OL,3,CGovernment scraps Devon warships HMS
OL,4,CAlbion and Bulwark
OL,6,FEarlier this year, Labour, in
OL,7,Fopposition, fought for the warships to
OL,8,Fremain in service.
OL,10,FLuke Pollard, Plymouth Sutton &
OL,11,FDevonport's MP and now Defence
OL,12,FMinister, previously said scrapping
OL,13,FHMS Albion and HMS Bulwark would be
OL,14,F"bad for Plymouth and bad for the
OL,15,FRoyal Navy."
OL,17,FBut now Labour insists that technology
OL,18,Fis "changing the nature of warfare"
OL,19,Fand "defence needs increased
OL,20,Fresilience and readiness for the
OL,21,Ffuture".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
