OL,3,CGovernment scraps Devon warships HMS
OL,4,CAlbion and Bulwark
OL,6,FRichard Foord, Lib Dem MP for Honiton
OL,7,F& Sidmouth said: "I welcome today's
OL,8,Femphasis on our service people.
OL,10,F"The previous government neglected the
OL,11,Fcritical importance of retaining armed
OL,12,Fforces personnel, leading to alarming
OL,13,Fgaps in capability.
OL,15,F"I particularly welcome the #8,000
OL,16,Fretention package for Army personnel
OL,17,Fwith over four years of service,
OL,18,Faddressing the Conservatives' legacy
OL,19,Fof low morale and poor retention rates.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
