OL,3,CGovernment scraps Devon warships HMS
OL,4,CAlbion and Bulwark
OL,6,F"However, significant concerns remain
OL,7,Fover the decision to decommission
OL,8,Fvital defence equipment.
OL,10,F"Skilled Leonardo employees in Yeovil
OL,11,Fare none the wiser about the new
OL,12,Fmedium helicopter contract, despite
OL,13,Fthe retirement of the Puma.
OL,15,F"The decommissioning of HMS Albion and
OL,16,FHMS Bulwark is particularly concerning.
OL,18,F"Replacement ships are not due to come
OL,19,Finto service until 2033. I am
OL,20,Fconcerned about how it may limit the
OL,21,Fway that the Royal Marines can operate.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
